nodes.text: Area D-435 was a hyperspace quadrant in the Endor system.

Little to nothing was known about this quadrant. It was uncharacteristic and safe for travel. However, it was best for travelers to keep navigation computers alert for unexpected enemies in the area. The quadrant was typically inhabited by Alliance Pilots and bodyguards of the Trader's Guild. It was also the closest hyperspace quadrant to the Endor Space Station.
